                      "Description": "Only contacts with lifecycle_stage 'Customer' should be evaluated. Leads, prospects, and other stages must be ignored."
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "row_id": 4,
                    "cells": {
                      "Rule": "Contract Renewal Hold",
                      "Description": "Customers with notes indicating they are in active contract renewal negotiations must be excluded from automated churn outreach. Outreach during renewal could undermine the sales process."
